text: The surname Alphonse may refer to: *Alexandre Alphonse (born 1982), French- born Guadeloupean footballer *Eloi Maxime Alphonse, Malagasy diplomat and Ambassador of Madagascar to Russia *Gerard A. Alphonse (born 1972), American journalist *Mickaël Alphonse (born 1989), French footballer *Nadine Alphonse (born 1983), retired Canadian female volleyball player *S. title: Alphonse (surname)
